      "instruction": "<p>While the rice is cooking, peel and finely dice your <strong>red onion[s]</strong></p><p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a low heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>diced red onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and cook for 10 min or until slightly softened</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1677167551688-x200.jpg",
