      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>smoky</strong> <strong>lean pork chilli</strong> over the <strong>herby rice</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>popped beans</strong> and <strong>grated cheese</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
